{"word":"ναυτιάω","slug":"ναυτιάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ναυτιάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ναυτία'><el>ναυτία</el></a>\n<el>(ναυτιάω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><i>to be qualmish, suffer from seasickness</i> or <i>nausea</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}